&lt;p&gt;The expected OTE range for this role is &lt;span data-sheets-root=&quot;1&quot;&gt;$135,600&lt;/span&gt; - &lt;span data-sheets-root=&quot;1&quot;&gt;$169,500&lt;/span&gt;. The starting wage will depend on a number of factors including the candidate’s location, skills, experience, market demands, and internal pay parity. The OTE figure listed here includes base salary and commissions, which may or may not be earned depending on performance.&amp;nbsp; Depending on the position offered, equity and other forms of compensation may be provided as part of a total compensation package.&lt;/p&gt;
